window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Diver James McGregor is used to exploring sunken ships. But there's something strange about the wreck of the <i>Grave Descend</i>. No one aboard tells quite the same story about what happened. Then there's the mysterious cargo they were carrying.... </p> <p>In one of the most beautiful places on Earth, a sinister plot is about to unfold. And if McGregor's not careful, he may find himself in over his head. </p>"; 
